bbpress:

(1) Install webserver 
	See install.apache
- also, needs the php5-gd library
  aptitude install php5-gd

(2) Install mysql-server
aptitude install mysql-server

(3) Download and unzip wordpress
- download
http://bbpress.org/download/

(4) Set up wordpress database for site

CREATE DATABASE fishhouse_bbpress;
 
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON fishhouse_bbpress.* TO "fishhouse_bbuser"@"localhost" IDENTIFIED BY "password";
  
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

(5) Run the installer and follow instructions
 - For now, skip the bbpress integration
